environmental_stressor: Habitat destruction of traditional migration corridors due
  to industrial agriculture expansion and climate-shifted growing seasons disrupting
  generational knowledge transmission
family_situation: Daughter lives in Dallas, unable to return due to visa restrictions.
  Son works in a vertical farm in Mexico City, no longer following seasonal patterns.
  Husband died in 2034 from pesticide exposure while working treated fields.
