vulnerability_details: Like monarchs whose multi-generational migration cycle was
  broken, Elena's family's traditional seasonal movement between Mexico and agricultural
  communities in the US Midwest has been severed by border restrictions and habitat
  destruction. Her grandmother's knowledge of traditional waypoints and seasonal timing
  died with her during the 2035 heat dome, leaving Elena unable to complete the cultural
  transmission cycle her family maintained for six generations.
